section.p: Dworkin Bariman. He is small, strong built old humpback. He is the architect of the basic Pattern and directly of Amber. It is written that he originally came from Courts of Chaos. He is father of Oberona and the grandfather of all other Amberits. Dworkin has drawn initial Trumps of family of Amber, has drawn the basic Pattern, has deciphered the book of the Unicorn. His symbol - the Pattern.
Oberon. (Apparently he is dead, died while trying to repair the Pattern.) Father of "senior" generation
of Amberits
. His symbol - five-pointed crown of Amber.

Benedict. Oberon's oldest son, Master of Arms at the courts of Amber. Lord-protector of Avalon during the Patternfall war. High, thin, a long powerful jaw, brown eyes, smooth brown hair. Colors of clothes: orange, yellow and brown. His symbol - Sunflower.
Brightly red hair, dark blue eyes, a bearded, small chin. Colors of clothes: red and orange. Carries usually silk and a plenty of jewelry. His symbol - the open book of spells.

(Apparently he is dead, killed by Caine). Green eyes, red hair, a short chin, he is not tall. Color of clothes: green. Owner of Werewindle, day sword which contains image of the burning edge of the Pattern. He has undergone to full ritual becoming living trump. His symbol - a falling star on a background of stars.
Caine. (He is apparently dead, killed by the Rinaldo/Luke.) Swarty, dark eyes. Colors of clothes: black and green. His symbol - the seagull on a background of the night sky in a storm.

Corwin. (Carl Corey, Cordell Fenneval [in France]). Green eyes, black hair. Weighs approximately 200 pounds. Looks thirtish. Colors of clothes: black and silver. Owner of Grayswandir, night blade with an imprint of a lunar edge of the Pattern. His symbol - a silver rose.

Eric. (Apparently he is dead, killed by manticora while defending Amber.) Dark blue-black hair, bearded, he is very handsome. Colors of clothes: red and black. His symbol - the crossed swords on a background of the full moon on completely black sky.
Deirdre. (Apparently dead, dragged from the cliff by Brand). Long black hair and dark blue eyes. Colors of clothes: black with silver. Her symbol - a half moon.
Fionea (Fi). Red hair, green eyes, 5 ' 2 ". Colors of clothes: green, pale - lilac, violet. Her symbol - the white circle with pentagon turned upside-down in it, on a black background.

Florimel (Flora, Evelyn Flaumel). Gold hair, dark blue eyes. Colors of clothes: green and grey. Has some the Irish wolfhounds, with nicknames Donner, Blitzen, etc. the Symbol - a lotus flower on a background with a falling sun.

Gerard (the Defender of the seas of the Gold Circle). Green eyes, black hair, a short beard and light moustaches, looks similar to Corwin, but is larger than him, and he has a stronger jaw. Colors of clothes: dark blue and grey with black. His symbol - a chalice. His symbol as specified in "War" is a bronze three-mast a vessel.

Julian (Defender of Arden forest). Long dark hair, dark blue eyes. Carries an armour painted in white. Colors of clothes: white and black. A symbol - the attacking hunting hawk. The tree is specified in as his symbol in "War".
Random (Now king of Amber). 5 ' 6 ", 135 pounds. Blond hair, sharp nose, a laughing mouth. Colors of clothes: orange, red, and brown. His symbol - a small set of drums with a drum-type stick on them.

Merlin (Merl Corey). Black hair, dark blue eyes, muscular. Colors of clothes: grey and violet. Learned sorcery and skill of creation of trumps at Courts of Chaos. He has passed the Pattern and Logrus. Now king in Courts of Chaos. His symbol - a vertical white pentagon on a background of a dark circle. Now carries one Spikard and has the second. The son or Dara Sawall and Corwin.

Rinaldo (Lucas Raynard/Luke). Son of Brend and queen Jasra. He has undergone to small ritual of increase of power in the Keep of Four Worlds. Now king of Kashfa. His symbol - a phoenix, rising from a flame. Colors of clothes: green. He is closely acquainted with Courts of Chaos as his mother was recruited from nearby shadow by Dara.
Martin. Son of Rendom and Morganthe from Rebma. Now punker, which is reflected in his manner of clothing. His symbol - reflection of the Earth in an aura of radiating beams.

Vialle (Queen of Amber) 5'1", slim, brunette, fine featured and soft spoken. She is the wife of Random she is the blind sculptress that he was forced to marry in Rebma but has since grown to love. She is adept in the healing arts and has uncanny perception despite her disability (able to use Trumps). Her symbol is of crashing waves.

Sawall, Dara (Mistress Of The Logrus) Tall and thin with short brown hair and freckles, dark eyes. Mother of Merlin, Jurt and Despil. Wife of Rim-Duke Gramble Sawall. She has essayed the Logrus and walked the Pattern. Possibly the great grand-daughter of Benedict. Father was of House Helgram, mother was of House Hendrake. Her symbol is a circle divided lengthwise, left side black and right side white.

Sawall, Mandor. Son of Sawall and Another. Powerful sorcerer from the courts who uses metal balls as a foci. Very dignified and regal. Has white hair and distinguishing/noble characteristics. Symbol is four squares of a chessboard, two black and two white, the white squares diagonal from each other and containing a black pawn in the upper left hand square and a black knight in the lower right hand square all contained within a circle.

Bright blond hair, large, very muscular. Colors of clothes: black and green. The sworn enemy of Amber because his mother was probably raped by Oberon. A symbol - a heraldic lion, rendering a unicorn which he carries as a medallion on a neck. Originally from Eregnor.
